Text.Value: Come to me. I want you.
Such splendour... how did I live without it?
This music! To live for... To die for...
So beautiful. Like the whispers of the succubi.
Such rapturous music. I can hardly resist...
No more blood. No more killing. Just this, please.
Is that you, Mystra? It is you! Sing! Sing on!
Malcanthet herself did not sound so sweet.
Sing your dark hymn to me, Shar. Never stop.

EditorData.NodeContext: Enchanted - on Karlach node, 'Malcanthet' is pronounced 'MAL-can-fet'

Text.Value: I could listen to this forever...
I could drown in that song...
I'll be there soon, my lady.
Closer... I need to get closer!
Play on! Play on and soothe my soul!
I can't resist... don't want to.
Such sweet music... I must listen...
I've never heard something so beautiful...

Synopsis: AD when the player is charmed by the harpies.
